          }
        ]
      },
      "sheet": "At the start of each of your turns, you regain {{survivor:hp}} hp if you have no more than half of your hp left. You don't gain this benefit if you have 0 hp.",
      "source": "Player's Handbook",
      "type": "Archetype Feature"
